{"tid":1530413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［頂置］901 三罷 即時討論 （1）","createTime":"2019-09-02T03:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T05:21:55.000Z","uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"be0f57935119b360221a7101f690c3b1f41b4a63","tid":1530413,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:04:58.000Z","msg":"全日資訊集中係一個post內討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KYd1XC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KYd1XC.jpg&h=a20c6b65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7td1XD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7td1XD.jpg&h=353e8267&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b221f7ddf340c4920938d44f9a2ec41a58d59bba","tid":1530413,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:05:24.000Z","msg":"大埔何中要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n急！大埔富善邨何中校長 聲稱會將罷課學生資料交給教育局 已fact check<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530398</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1f2fc61e976b5c9727c7f9ceb290700fb4296744","tid":1530413,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:06:59.000Z","msg":"如果警察濫暴政府冇辦法制衡，亦唔好期望校園欺凌會制止到，因為人與人之間嘅信任破壞咗，自然會產生無限嘅懷疑，警察子女極有可能成為欺凌者二代，將所有仇恨歸究普通市民子女。<br />\n<br />\n加上政府及其父母都不斷用歪理去灌輸佢地，強逼弱小心靈相信自己會被排斥，又點會同身邊嘅人好好相處呢？<br />\n<br />\n所以，真正想將暴力帶入校園嘅，係一直濫用暴力嘅政權，呢班大人用人民鬥人民嘅計謀，已經令社會撕裂，而家仲想令學生鬥學生，遺禍埋下一代。"},{"pid":"9e6f8ab19ef6dce0fdf53bc068161032b3497d78","tid":1530413,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86558f4045980cd80a136e87b938c451b5eb69f1","tid":1530413,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT